%H A397613 Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, <a href="https://mathworld.wolfram.com/Trapezohedron.html">Trapezohedron</a>.
%H A397613 Wikipedia, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hexagonal_trapezohedron">Hexagonal trapezohedron</a>.
%H A397613 <a href="/index/Tra#transcendental">Index entries for transcendental numbers</a>.
%F A397613 Equals arccos((7 - 3*sqrt(3))/2) = arccos((7 - A010482)/2).
%F A397613 Equals arccos(c), where c = 0.90192... is the smallest root of 2*x^2 - 14*x + 11.
